{"tid":2151024,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"下月25日起香港製造並出口美國商品須標明中國製造","createTime":"2020-08-11T07:44:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T10:00:02.000Z","uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c3a31026ba39012c3d7d1e8c92be7e09c0867813","tid":2151024,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T07:44:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543082-20200811.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543082-20200811.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9FpzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=77786df2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543082-20200811.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=2501e7f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543082-20200811.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普7月簽署行政命令，終止香港的特殊待遇地位後，美國海關和邊境保護局發布公告，宣布由9月25日起，所有香港製造並出口到美國的商品，必須貼上中國製造的標籤，表明原產地是中國。<br />\n<br />\n彭博通訊社分析說，新規例對香港貿易或經濟的實際影響有限，因為由香港直接出口美國的商品數量很少。根據特區政府統計，去年香港對美國出口額為3040億港元，當中只有大約1.2%為本土出口，近八成是內地經香港轉口美國。"},{"pid":"6b64e9f860cf557c404fc61b0aeef36410107ec2","tid":2151024,"uid":292644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T10:00:02.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\">以後港女嫁鬼佬，係咪要响塊閪度贴&quot;China west&quot; 呢個sticker?</span>"}]}